00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:01,420
so on the surface, the note says

575
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,730
you took the money.

576
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:05,090
But "jia" includes the character for pig,

577
00:28:05,790 --> 00:28:06,700
so what it really says

578
00:28:07,110 --> 00:28:08,180
is that a pig

579
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:10,090
took all the money.

580
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:22,220
When your family gathered to honor the ancestors,

581
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:25,010
you were out drinking.

582
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:27,660
The Marquis was disappointed and angry.

583
00:28:28,720 --> 00:28:29,530
Over time,

584
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:30,860
he'll lose

585
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:33,090
all faith in you.

586
00:28:37,830 --> 00:28:39,380
Was it your own choice to stay away,

587
00:28:40,030 --> 00:28:42,460
or did someone make sure you would?

588
00:28:47,270 --> 00:28:48,140
Mr. Zhixing,

589
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:50,700
how much longer are you going to put up

590
00:28:50,790 --> 00:28:51,940
with all this humiliation?

591
00:28:55,070 --> 00:28:55,900
Lady Jiang's kindness

592
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:57,940
is easy to accept

593
00:28:59,070 --> 00:28:59,940
but hard to reject.

594
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:05,050
Don't you want to fight?

595
00:29:07,110 --> 00:29:08,090
Fight for what?

596
00:29:11,440 --> 00:29:13,810
To prove you can surpass your brother.

597
00:29:20,350 --> 00:29:21,220
Do you really think

598
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:23,700
I can do it?

599
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:26,180
Of course.

600
00:29:26,830 --> 00:29:28,330
Your brother's mediocre in every way.

601
00:29:28,750 --> 00:29:30,140
He can't ease the Emperor's burdens.

602
00:29:30,550 --> 00:29:32,050
Nor can he win hearts.

603
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,180
Frankly, I think

604
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:36,220
he's already peaked.

605
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,900
If someone like him inherits

606
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:53,490
the title of the Marquis of Pingjin,

607
00:29:53,790 --> 00:29:56,380
the Zhuang family

608
00:29:56,550 --> 00:29:57,490
will only decline.

609
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,730
But you're different.

610
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:03,180
You're bold and free-spirited,

611
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,980
just like the Marquis in his youth.

612
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:08,490
One day, you'll lead armies and rise to the top.

613
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:15,860
Mr. Zhixing?

614
00:30:18,550 --> 00:30:19,090
Zang Hai,

615
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:20,980
no one's ever said

616
00:30:21,030 --> 00:30:22,290
anything like that to me.

617
00:30:24,790 --> 00:30:25,860
That makes me feel

618
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:28,250
even better than winning at the tables.

619
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:31,330
We must have a drink together.

620
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:32,050
All right.

621
00:30:32,110 --> 00:30:33,770
As you wish.

622
00:30:34,030 --> 00:30:35,770
Whatever you say, sir.

623
00:30:36,270 --> 00:30:36,770
Good.

624
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:48,460
Here.

625
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:51,420
This is the Tusu wine I've been saving at Zhen Tower.

626
00:30:51,790 --> 00:30:52,860
Have a taste.

627
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:54,940
Here.

628
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:55,980
Thank you, sir.

629
00:31:01,110 --> 00:31:01,660
Cheers.

630
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:10,050
Zang Hai,

631
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,900
you've been looking out for me,

632
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:13,530
but I doubt

633
00:31:14,550 --> 00:31:16,220
this is all for my sake.

634
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:18,090
There's something in it for you, right?

635
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:20,180
Your brother's current success

636
00:31:20,510 --> 00:31:21,330
owes everything

637
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:22,770
to Jiang Xiang's support.

638
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:25,420
Even if I joined his camp,

639
00:31:25,790 --> 00:31:27,140
at most I'd be

640
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:29,380
just another forgettable aide.

641
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,460
He'd never see me as anything more.

642
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:32,900
But with you, it's different.

643
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:35,220
You've got nothing to lose.

644
00:31:35,480 --> 00:31:36,660
So why not take a chance?

645
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,860
You see things clearly.

646
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:42,010
My brother's already in office,

647
00:31:42,310 --> 00:31:43,660
and he's my father's chosen heir.

648
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:46,940
You wouldn't get far helping him.

649
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:49,460
So you're betting on me instead.

650
00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:52,860
If it pays off,

651
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:53,810
you'll win big.

652
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:55,730
You know how to gamble.

653
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:57,980
I could never match you, Mr. Zhixing.

654
00:31:58,550 --> 00:31:59,220
Zang Hai,

655
00:31:59,590 --> 00:32:00,810
after talking to you today,

656
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:02,940
I realize there's actually

657
00:32:03,030 --> 00:32:05,460
someone in the family who cares about me.

658
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:06,090
Come on.

659
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:07,290
Here's to you.

660
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:11,570
You...

661
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:13,860
I don't hold my liquor well.

662
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,660
Do you think you're too good for my wine?

663
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:18,530
Of course not.

664
00:32:29,310 --> 00:32:29,730
Here.

665
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,420
This is indeed excellent wine.

666
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:43,940
I'm good at drinking.

667
00:32:44,590 --> 00:32:45,620
But I'm useless

668
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:48,050
when it comes to real work.

669
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,290
All I know is how to enjoy myself.

670
00:32:49,590 --> 00:32:50,940
I'm afraid I'll let you down.

671
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,330
You underestimate yourself, sir.

672
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:54,660
You don't believe me?

673
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:57,090
Let me tell you something.

674
00:32:58,350 --> 00:32:59,420
When I was a kid,

675
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:01,810
I was once locked in an underground tunnel

676
00:33:02,110 --> 00:33:02,900
by a bully.

677
00:33:03,590 --> 00:33:05,420
It was just one night, but I nearly died in there.

678
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:06,980
So no,

679
00:33:07,070 --> 00:33:08,900
I really can't handle hardship.

680
00:33:10,240 --> 00:33:13,050
That just means you're blessed, Mr. Zhixing.

681
00:33:13,590 --> 00:33:15,180
Surviving disaster means there's fortune ahead.

682
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:22,090
To this day, I still remember that bully.

683
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:24,530
Back then,

684
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,530
when trying to find his father,

685
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:28,420
he got whipped by the Princess of Dongxia.

686
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:30,380
He also seized me

687
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:32,290
to ask about his father's whereabouts.

688
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:37,140
Do you know who his father was?

689
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,700
How would I know that?

690
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:44,010
His name was Kuai Duo.

691
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:46,900
He was the Imperial Astronomer back then.

692
00:33:47,790 --> 00:33:49,730
But the very next day, his whole family was wiped out.

693
00:33:50,790 --> 00:33:52,380
The kid died too, of course.

694
00:33:56,590 --> 00:33:59,770
He had a deep wound on his back.

695
00:34:00,310 --> 00:34:03,900
They said it looked like a cross

696
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:04,730
or even a sword,

697
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:08,130
just like yours.

698
00:34:08,590 --> 00:34:10,130
You're not that bully, are you?

699
00:34:12,230 --> 00:34:13,690
You're too funny, Mr. Zhixing.

700
00:34:14,190 --> 00:34:15,380
The scars on my back?

701
00:34:15,670 --> 00:34:16,860
I got them when I was a kid.

702
00:34:17,110 --> 00:34:18,980
My master whipped me for slacking off.

703
00:34:20,550 --> 00:34:21,210
Is that so?

704
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:24,050
I guess it's true.

705
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,210
After all, he's long dead.

706
00:34:27,110 --> 00:34:28,460
If he'd lived,

707
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,170
he'd be about your age now.

708
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:34,900
He'd definitely find a way to get close to my father,

709
00:34:35,230 --> 00:34:36,460
and when the time is right,

710
00:34:37,070 --> 00:34:38,900
he'd kill him.

711
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:40,650
Mr. Zhixing,

712
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:42,300
you're

713
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:43,900
scaring me.

714
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:47,980
A bully and a massacre?

715
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:50,130
I don't understand a word of it.

716
00:34:50,710 --> 00:34:52,210
Like I said,

717
00:34:53,590 --> 00:34:54,650
I came to the Marquis's Mansion

718
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:57,980
just to find a place to settle in.

719
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:01,300
If anything were to happen to the Marquis,

720
00:35:02,710 --> 00:35:04,210
it wouldn't do me any good.

721
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:05,940
Wouldn't you agree?

722
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,690
Maybe you're just trying to secure a future.

723
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,340
Or maybe

724
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:14,980
you realized you couldn't kill my father,

725
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:19,860
so you changed tactics and came after me.

726
00:35:21,710 --> 00:35:22,690
Am I right...

727
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:25,570
Zhinu?

728
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:28,980
Admit it. You're Zhinu.

729
00:35:30,150 --> 00:35:31,170
You didn't die back then,

730
00:35:31,880 --> 00:35:33,380
and now you're back for revenge.

731
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:36,610
Mr. Zhixing,

732
00:35:37,510 --> 00:35:38,260
you've had too much to drink.

733
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:41,490
I'll say it again:

734
00:35:42,590 --> 00:35:43,780
You've got the wrong man.

735
00:35:44,440 --> 00:35:45,820
I'm not Zhinu.

736
00:35:46,550 --> 00:35:47,380
My name is Zang Hai.

737
00:35:48,510 --> 00:35:50,010
If you don't believe me,

738
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:52,010
you're welcome to investigate.

739
00:35:53,670 --> 00:35:55,010
I'm perfectly sober right now.

740
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:57,130
I'll tell you something.

741
00:35:58,030 --> 00:35:59,820
I've remembered you ever since we first met

742
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:00,780
in the treasury.

743
00:36:01,110 --> 00:36:03,340
Later, when Yang Zhen and Qu Jiao died because of you,

744
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:05,170
I started to become suspicious of you.

745
00:36:05,710 --> 00:36:09,300
This Tusu wine contains lovage rhizome and cinnamon.

746
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:11,340
Drinking it brings back all the scars,

747
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,460
no matter how long they've faded.

748
00:36:12,590 --> 00:36:13,380
Mr. Zhixing,

749
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:16,050
no one's going to believe your wild guesses.

750
00:36:16,070 --> 00:36:16,820
The scars on your back

751
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:17,860
are all the proof I need.

752
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:20,010
We can go right now

753
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:21,980
and show them to my father.

754
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:23,650
No matter who you are,

755
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:25,860
no matter how good you are with words,

756
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:28,780
I doubt he'll spare you.

757
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,940
If you already figured it out,

758
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,490
why are you just telling me?

759
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:47,690
Because my father's hands

760
00:36:47,710 --> 00:36:49,210
are already stained with your family's blood.

761
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:51,170
I don't want him to kill you too.

762
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:56,260
That night ten years ago,

763
00:36:57,110 --> 00:36:58,380
I couldn't sleep after what you did

764
00:36:58,840 --> 00:36:59,490
to me.

765
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:01,130
- Father? - So I wanted

766
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:02,170
to have my father stand up for me.

767
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:05,490
Father?

768
00:37:06,320 --> 00:37:07,300
But then I got tired,

769
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:09,300
so I waited outside his room.

770
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:11,340
He came back very late.

771
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:13,050
I wanted to call out to him,

772
00:37:13,670 --> 00:37:15,490
but his face was grim.

773
00:37:15,550 --> 00:37:16,010
Father...

774
00:37:16,230 --> 00:37:16,820
I knew

775
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:19,570
something must have happened that night.

776
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:25,820
Young Master, where are you going

777
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:26,570
this early?

778
00:37:26,710 --> 00:37:27,300
To visit the Kuai family.

779
00:37:27,670 --> 00:37:28,460
The Kuai family?

780
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:31,900
Young Master,

781
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:33,340
which Kuai family?

782
00:37:33,710 --> 00:37:34,820
Which one do you think?

783
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:37,340
The Imperial Astronomer's. They live in the suburbs.

784
00:37:38,150 --> 00:37:39,900
Their residence caught fire last night.

785
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:42,780
Everyone inside died.

786
00:37:47,280 --> 00:37:48,380
But then I remembered the look

787
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:49,420
on my father's face

788
00:37:50,550 --> 00:37:51,820
and the burn marks

789
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:53,340
on Yang Zhen's robes that night.

790
00:37:54,190 --> 00:37:55,300
That's when I started to suspect

791
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:57,860
my father was

792
00:37:59,230 --> 00:38:00,210
behind those deaths.

793
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:02,490
But I didn't dare think that.

794
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,530
What if it was true?

795
00:38:09,190 --> 00:38:09,940
Zhinu,

796
00:38:11,760 --> 00:38:13,570
I know you've had it rough these years.

797
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:15,090
I know you hate my father.

798
00:38:15,590 --> 00:38:16,900
But I can't let you take revenge.

799
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,530
He's the only family I have left.

800
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:24,210
If you try to kill him,

801
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,340
I will kill you first.

802
00:38:32,030 --> 00:38:34,420
Leave the Marquis's Mansion. Leave the Capital.

803
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:36,170
And never come back.

804
00:38:38,710 --> 00:38:39,820
And if I can't?

805
00:38:43,670 --> 00:38:45,460
You've got one day.

806
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:04,420
How did he find out?

807
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:07,090
He's smarter than I thought.

808
00:39:07,840 --> 00:39:09,570
He took notice of me when we first met

809
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:10,740
in the treasury.

810
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:13,260
After I took out Yang Zhen and Qu Jiao,

811
00:39:13,590 --> 00:39:14,900
he began to suspect me.

812
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:17,340
He never saw the scars on my back,

813
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:19,490
but he remembered how my senior brothers

814
00:39:19,510 --> 00:39:20,300
described them.

815
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:22,820
The scars had faded,

816
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,780
but today at Zhen Tower,

817
00:39:25,110 --> 00:39:26,820
he made me drink some medicinal wine,

818
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:29,130
and then the two scars reappeared.

819
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:32,490
I planned to deny everything,

820
00:39:32,710 --> 00:39:34,210
but he threatened to take me to the Marquis.

821
00:39:35,110 --> 00:39:36,820
With how suspicious the Marquis is,

822
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:38,210
I'd be dead for sure.

823
00:39:42,590 --> 00:39:45,130
These problems never end. What do we do now?

824
00:39:47,670 --> 00:39:49,260
Zhuang Zhixing didn't turn me in.

825
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:51,980
He pitied me and gave me one day

826
00:39:52,110 --> 00:39:53,820
to leave the Marquis's Mansion and the Capital.

827
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:56,780
One day?

828
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:02,690
You're visiting the ancestral tombs with the Marquis tomorrow.

829
00:40:04,030 --> 00:40:05,340
Zhuang Zhixing will be there too.

830
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:07,300
While you're there,

831
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:09,090
he'll definitely be alone at some point.

832
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:10,260
Let Guanfeng and Shilei

833
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:11,860
find a chance to kill him.

834
00:40:11,920 --> 00:40:13,900
He's not a bad man. He doesn't deserve to die.

835
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:14,980
Getting soft, are you?

836
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,090
I'm not.

837
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:20,210
You hesitate to kill the innocent,

838
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:23,050
but did the Marquis spare anyone in your family?

839
00:40:23,550 --> 00:40:24,530
Zhuang Zhixing is

840
00:40:24,550 --> 00:40:25,820
just like a powder keg.

841
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:27,650
Let him live, and you risk your revenge

842
00:40:27,670 --> 00:40:28,780
and your life!

843
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:29,460
I know!

844
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:35,090
I'll take care of it.

845
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:37,170
If he has to die,

846
00:40:38,230 --> 00:40:39,380
I'll kill him myself.

847
00:41:18,340 --> 00:41:19,020
[Late mother Shen's grave]

848
00:41:19,030 --> 00:41:19,900
Mother,

849
00:41:21,230 --> 00:41:22,210
I've come to see you.

850
00:41:30,590 --> 00:41:31,690
The servants did

851
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:32,690
such a poor job.

852
00:41:34,550 --> 00:41:35,860
They didn't pull the weeds

853
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:37,460
or refill the soil.

854
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:39,380
I'll scold them when I get back.

855
00:41:41,190 --> 00:41:42,460
Are you doing well down there?

856
00:41:44,630 --> 00:41:47,090
I'm fine. Don't worry about me.

857
00:41:48,510 --> 00:41:49,900
Father's visiting the tombs tomorrow.

858
00:41:51,190 --> 00:41:52,460
I'll ask him to stop by your grave too.

859
00:42:00,400 --> 00:42:01,460
Lady Jiang treats me well.

860
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:03,260
She's never harmed me,

861
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:05,420
but she's always on guard,

862
00:42:06,670 --> 00:42:07,940
trying to raise me into a useless man

863
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:09,210
so I won't compete with my brother.

864
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:13,420
But she worries too much.

865
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:15,860
I've never even thought of it.

866
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:49,610
And I ran into an old face.

867
00:42:50,150 --> 00:42:51,650
I know he came back

868
00:42:52,030 --> 00:42:53,820
to kill Father and avenge his family.

869
00:42:55,280 --> 00:42:56,260
I told him to leave the Capital

870
00:42:57,280 --> 00:42:58,260
and never come back.

871
00:43:22,260 --> 00:43:26,940
Conceal the ambition in my eyes

872
00:43:29,460 --> 00:43:36,100
In my palm, I hold a dangerous desire

873
00:43:36,660 --> 00:43:39,420
Turbulent waves hidden in my sleeves

874
00:43:40,020 --> 00:43:42,740
Silent thunder echoes around

875
00:43:43,020 --> 00:43:44,980
However cunning you are

876
00:43:45,460 --> 00:43:47,540
I can see

877
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:51,380
Right through you

878
00:43:57,740 --> 00:44:04,780
Schemes are my armor

879
00:44:04,940 --> 00:44:10,380
Overt plans are my weapons

880
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:14,660
With restrained fury

881
00:44:15,340 --> 00:44:18,020
I purge the world's corruption

882
00:44:18,220 --> 00:44:20,260
The night is not dark

883
00:44:20,740 --> 00:44:22,820
Because

884
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:29,420
My heart burns bright

885
00:44:32,220 --> 00:44:35,500
I control the shifting clouds

886
00:44:35,700 --> 00:44:38,260
I command the falling rain

887
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:40,780
The compass of the human soul is unpredictable

888
00:44:40,900 --> 00:44:45,700
There will always be ups and downs

889
00:44:46,180 --> 00:44:49,500
I hold the power of life and death

890
00:44:49,700 --> 00:44:52,260
I grant and I take away

891
00:44:52,420 --> 00:44:55,940
When faith burns like the scorching sun

892
00:44:55,980 --> 00:44:59,460
I will sing aloud with you

893
00:44:59,580 --> 00:45:02,820
I am the sowing season

894
00:45:02,940 --> 00:45:06,220
I am the autumn harvest

895
00:45:06,460 --> 00:45:08,620
I am the world

896
00:45:08,820 --> 00:45:12,380
I am the people

897
00:45:13,580 --> 00:45:16,660
And you are also me
